# 弹窗接口开发
接口集成，将HTML、CSS、JS进行分离，尽可能重用组件，提高接口的重用度。

## 简单弹窗效果

```
popupText("提示文字");

function popupText(Describe,Time){
    var oDiv = document.createElement("div");
    oDiv.id = "popup";
    var sText = "font-size: 12px;z-index: 999;position: fixed;max-width:80%;left:50%;top:50%;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.8);color:#FFF;padding:16px 20px;border-radius:6px;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);-webkit-transform:translate(-50%,-50%);"
    var textHtml = '<div style="' + sText + '" class="popup_text">' + Describe +'</div>';
    oDiv.innerHTML = textHtml;
    document.body.appendChild(oDiv);
    if(Time == undefined){
        Time = 1000;
    }
    setTimeout(function(){
        document.body.removeChild(document.getElementById("popup"));
    },Time);
}
```

```
.popup_text{
    position: fixed;
    max-width:80%;
    left:50%;
    top:50%;
    background:rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
    color:#FFF;
    padding:16px 20px;
    border-radius:6px;
    transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
    -webkit-transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
}
```

## 加载弹窗效果

功能：简单的加载效果
```
tipLoading("加载中...")

function tipLoading(Describe){
    //样式
    var sText = document.createElement('style');
    sText.type = 'text/css';
    var dataImg = 'data:image/png;base64,';
    sText.setAttribute('data-name','tip-loading');
    sText.innerHTML =  '.loading_text{z-index: 999;position: fixed;display: inline-block;left: 50%;top: 50%;transform: translate(-50%,-50%);-webkit-transform: translate(-50%,-50%);padding: 9px 20px;border-radius: 5px;color: #FFF;background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);}'
        + '.loading_text .texts{margin-left: 10px;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 14px;}'
        + '.loading_text .icon_loading{display: inline-block;width: 24px;height: 24px;vertical-align: middle;}'
        + '.loading_text .icon_loading:before {content: "";display: block;width: 100%;height: 100%;background: url("'+ dataImg +'") no-repeat;-webkit-background-size: 24px auto;-webkit-animation: rotate linear 1s infinite;animation: rotate linear 1s infinite;}'
        + '@-webkit-keyframes rotate {0% {-webkit-transform:rotate(0deg);transform:rotate(0deg)}100% {-webkit-transform:rotate(360deg);transform:rotate(360deg)}}';
    document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0].appendChild(sText);
    // 元素
    var oDiv = document.createElement('div');
    oDiv.id = 'tip_loading';
    var textHtml = '<div class="loading_text"><span class="icon_loading"></span><span class="texts">'+ Describe +'</span></div>';
    oDiv.innerHTML = textHtml;
    document.body.appendChild(oDiv);
    // oDiv.style.display = 'none';
}
```


功能：实现数据加载中，用户交互提示。可以自行设置消失时间，提示文字。
```
//提示信息：时间10000:10s 时间可以为空值；
popupLoad("","亲，我们正在努力加载…");

function popupLoad(Time,Describe){
    var oDiv = document.createElement("div");
    oDiv.id = "bPopupLoad";
    var textHtml = '<div class="TipLoad"><div class="loadimg"></div><p class="loadp">' + Describe +'</p></div>'
    oDiv.innerHTML = textHtml;
    document.body.appendChild(oDiv);
    if(Time !== ""){
        setTimeout(function(){
            document.body.removeChild(document.getElementById("bPopupLoad"));
        },Time);
    }
}
```


```
<div class="TipLoad"><div class="loadimg"></div><p class="loadp">亲，我们正在努力加载…</p></div>

//popupFun(aFun1,aFun2,"标题","描述");
当fA、fB等为空时，自动清空弹窗，标题必须填写，描述可选。

function popupFun(oCancel,oConfirm,oTitle,oDescribe){
    if(oDescribe == undefined){oDescribe = "";}
    //结构
    var oTexts = "";
    var oDiv = document.createElement("div");
    oDiv.id = "TipConF";
    oTexts = '<div class="TipConF"><div class="Title"><div class="H1"><strong>' + oDescribe +'</strong></div><div class="H2">' + oTitle +'</div><div class="Btns"><a href="javascript:;" id="Offs" class="Off">取消</a><a href="javascript:;" id="Ons" class="On">确定</a></div></div></div>'
    oDiv.innerHTML = oTexts;
    document.body.appendChild(oDiv);
    // 移除
    var bOffs = document.getElementById("Offs");
    var bOns = document.getElementById("Ons");
    bOffs.onclick = function(){
        document.body.removeChild(oDiv);
        oCancel();
    }
    bOns.onclick = function(){
        document.body.removeChild(oDiv);
        oConfirm();
    }
}
function aFun1(){
    console.log("Cancel");
}
function aFun2(){
    console.log("Confirm");
}

## 横屏提示信息

```
mobileRotate("为了更好的体验，请将手机/平板竖过来");

function mobileRotate(Describe){
    //样式
    var sText = document.createElement('style');
    sText.type = 'text/css';
    var dataImg = 'data:image/png;base64,';
    sText.innerHTML = '.mob-con{width: 100%;height: 100%;position: absolute;left: 0;top: 0;background: #32373b;z-index: 9990;}.mob-cen{position: absolute;left: 50%;top: 50%;transform: translate(-50%,-50%);-webkit-transform: translate(-50%,-50%);z-index: 9999;}.mob-cen i{margin: auto;display: block;width: 128px;height: 194px;background: url(' + dataImg + ');background-size: 128px 194px;animation: mobileR 1.5s ease infinite alternate;-webkit-animation: mobileR 1.5s ease infinite alternate;}.mob-cen div{font-size: 22px;margin-top: 20px;color: #ffd40a;}@keyframes mobileR{0% {-webkit-transform: rotate(-90deg);}30% {-webkit-transform: rotate(-90deg);}70% {-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);}100% {-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);}}@-webkit-keyframes mobileR{0% {-webkit-transform: rotate(-90deg);}30% {-webkit-transform: rotate(-90deg);}70% {-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);}100% {-webkit-transform: rotate(0deg);}}';
    document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0].appendChild(sText);
    // 元素
    var oDiv = document.createElement('div');
    oDiv.id = 'MoblileR';
    var textHtml = '<div class="mob-con"><div class="mob-cen"><i></i><div>'+ Describe +'</div></div></div>';
    oDiv.innerHTML = textHtml;
    document.body.appendChild(oDiv);
    oDiv.style.display = 'none';

    window.addEventListener('onorientationchange' in window ? 'orientationchange' : 'resize',function(){
            var oMobs = '';
            if(document.documentElement.clientHeight >= document.documentElement.clientWidth){
                oMobs = 'protrait';
            }else{
                oMobs = 'landscape';
            }
            var MoblieR = document.getElementById('MoblileR');
            if(oMobs == 'protrait'){
                MoblieR.style.display = 'none';
            }else{
                MoblieR.style.display = 'block';
            }
        setTimeout(function(){
        },200);
    })
}
